video_title: Growth always hurts, do you agree? #growth #mindset #positivity #adviceoftheday
transcript:
very few people are going to tell you
this but growth hurts becoming the best
version of yourself comes with a lot of
goodbyes sadly the only way for some

yourself with toxic people because
you're lonely it's really

today though is going to be the power
